Architecture: any
Suggests: kno-docs
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libu8 (>= 2.6.7-83), libzip4 | libzip2, libarchive13, libsnappy1v5, libzstd1, libssl1.1 | libssl1.0 | libssl1.0.0, libcurl4 | libcurl3, libhyphen0, libedit2, adduser, libldns2 | libldns1, libjemalloc1
Description: This package provides the core libraries, executables, and 
  configuration files for Kno applications

